[557.480397, "o", "\u001b[4mSORT\u001b[24m(1)                        User Commands                        \u001b[4mSORT\u001b[24m(1)\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mNAME\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n       sort - sort lines of text files\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mSYNOPSIS\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n       \u001b[1msort \u001b[22m[\u001b[4mOPTION\u001b[24m]... [\u001b[4mFILE\u001b[24m]...\u001b[m\r\n       \u001b[1msort \u001b[22m[\u001b[4mOPTION\u001b[24m]... \u001b[4m--files0-from=F\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mDESCRIPTION\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n       Write sorted concatenation of all FILE(s) to standard output.\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n       With no FILE, or when FILE is -, read standard input.\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n       Mandatory  arguments to long options are mandatory for short options\u001b[m\r\n       too.  Ordering options:\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n       \u001b[1m-b\u001b[22m, \u001b[1m--ignore-leading-blanks\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n              ignore leading blanks\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n       \u001b[1m-d\u001b[22m, \u001b[1m--dictionary-order\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[7m Manual page sort(1) line 1 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K"]
