[997.328354, "o", "\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KA\bA\r\u001b[K\u001b[H\u001bM       may want to sort the input first, or use 'sort \u001b[1m-u\u001b[22m' without 'uniq'.\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[22;1H\r\u001b[K\u001b[7m Manual page uniq(1) line 61/84 95% (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K"]
