[1032.04496, "o", "\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KB\bB\r\u001b[K              select only these fields;  also print any line that  contains\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[7m Manual page cut(1) line 7 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K"]
