[1162.203584, "o", "\u001b[4mTR\u001b[24m(1)                          User Commands                          \u001b[4mTR\u001b[24m(1)\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mNAME\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n       tr - translate or delete characters\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mSYNOPSIS\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n       \u001b[1mtr \u001b[22m[\u001b[4mOPTION\u001b[24m]... \u001b[4mSTRING1\u001b[24m [\u001b[4mSTRING2\u001b[24m]\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mDESCRIPTION\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n       Translate,  squeeze,  and/or  delete characters from standard input,\u001b[m\r\n       writing to standard output.  STRING1 and STRING2 specify  arrays  of\u001b[m\r\n       characters ARRAY1 and ARRAY2 that control the action.\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n       \u001b[1m-c\u001b[22m, \u001b[1m-C\u001b[22m, \u001b[1m--complement\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n              use the complement of ARRAY1\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n       \u001b[1m-d\u001b[22m, \u001b[1m--delete\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n              delete characters in ARRAY1, do not translate\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n       \u001b[1m-s\u001b[22m, \u001b[1m--squeeze-repeats\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n              replace  each sequence of a repeated character that is listed\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[7m Manual page tr(1) line 1 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K"]
